cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper discusses recent advancements in natural language processing using deep learning, with a special focus on transfer learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses various deep learning architectures and methods, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper mentions the ImageNet moment, which is a well-known concept in computer vision, indicating that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
